{"tid":2097285,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"軍情動態》震懾南海！美軍2航艦打擊群並肩操演 壯觀場面曝光","createTime":"2020-07-06T16:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T16:44:32.000Z","uid":177168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"80f0be5f777be8a91a07bc7ab0d2e2be49ead5e3","tid":2097285,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/07/06/phpdzfdsn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F07%2F06%2Fphpdzfdsn.jpg&h=88fa3a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">美國海軍尼米茲號航艦戰鬥群與雷根號航艦戰鬥群進軍南海，7月4日起，進行大規模演習，美軍今天公布兩艘航艦並肩航行，伴隨打擊群艦艇與各自空中機隊的畫面，相當震撼。（圖擷取自美軍第七艦隊官網）</code></pre><br />\n2020-07-06 23:23:13<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕針對中國企圖在南海擴張版圖，美國海軍尼米茲號航艦打擊群與雷根號航艦打擊群7月4日起在南海大規模演習，美軍今（6）日公布兩艘航艦、伴隨艦群與空中機隊並列的壯觀畫面；另外，也傳出在美軍操演期間，中國海軍的艦隊就在不遠處與美軍艦群遙遙互望。<br />\n綜合外媒報導，尼米茲號（USS Nimitz，CVN-68）航艦自6月17日抵達美軍第七艦隊管轄區後，就一直在大平洋-印度洋海域作例行巡航，執行維護安全與穩定的行動，期間也多次與雷根號航空母艦（USS Ronald Reagan CVN-76）進行演練。<br />\n中國海軍7月1日起在南海的西沙群島爭議海域展開5天演習，美軍也不甘示弱，尼米茲號航艦所屬的「第11航艦打擊群」（CSG-11）與雷根號航空母艦所屬的「第7航艦打擊群」（CSG-7）直接開拔進入南海，還選在美國獨立紀念日7月4日進行大規模演習，除了2艘排水量各10萬噸的航艦，各可載運約90架戰機，兩個打擊群的艦隊合計有約1萬2000名水手；這場綜合演習中，包括防空、戰術執行、模擬遠程海上打擊、戰機與艦隊的聯合作戰能力，以保持美國海軍的戰鬥準備與海上優勢。<br />\n雙航艦作戰提供了更大的作戰範圍，並在空戰中提高了戰力投射的速度與續戰力，2艘航艦的艦載機聯隊也進行全天候數百次的升降訓練；不過美軍在訓練期間，與中國海軍雙方也處於互相可目視的距離。第11航艦打擊群指揮官柯克（James Kirk）少將表示，「我們看得到他們，他們也看得到我們」，不過雙方接觸沒有發生任何意外。<br />\n美軍太平洋艦隊臉書貼文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/USPacificFleet/posts/10158356838002970\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUSPacificFleet%2Fposts%2F10158356838002970&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEqHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=17480aa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/USPacificFleet/posts/10158356838002970</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3219910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3219910&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEqHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=1d02b7e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3219910&h=84f44b01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3219910</a>"},{"pid":"bc2412bd66e4385ff594ec4e8bff953fa631c2a7","tid":2097285,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"禾郭刀有liu ling ho同山東 ho<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1bd7e28acacfab9a93c9e74fe5f930c62db3b1","tid":2097285,"uid":157525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc2412bd66e4385ff594ec4e8bff953fa631c2a7","tid":2097285,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"禾郭刀有liu ling ho同山東 ho<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:25:44.000Z","msg":"果2架影唔到相啦<br />\n剩係影到黑煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e3278aa0f93ce7e81ad46d9ff9061971afa012","tid":2097285,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc2412bd66e4385ff594ec4e8bff953fa631c2a7","tid":2097285,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"禾郭刀有liu ling ho同山東 ho<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zRuk5Yv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzRuk5Yv.png&h=8ca596fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dafa56e57d35c1c73daef2b88309553dc04aed0","tid":2097285,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:27:58.000Z","msg":"細細個已經聽過尼米兹號<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif